    <link href="/css/jquery.qtip.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/libraries/jquery.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/libraries/jquery.qtip.min.js"></script>
  </head>
  
  <body>

    <div class="container-fluid">
      <div class="content row">      
        <div class='span12'>
          <h2>Summary of California Water Rights</h2>
          <p></p>          

        
          <div class='span3 block observation'>
            <span class='large'>Total Number Current Water Rights: <%= count %></span>

            <p>Includes: Active, Adjudicated, Certified, Licensed, Pending, Permitted and Registered water Rights.</p>
            <p>Does not include: Riparian, Pre-1914, Inactive or Claimed rights.</p>
          </div>
        
          <div class='span6 block observation'>

    

<!--
      <div class='span3'>
        <span class='large'>Total Number Active Water Rights: <%= watermapApp.tally.count_active %></span>
        <p>May include some riparian and pre-1914 rights.</p>
        <span class='large'>Total Number Water Rights: <%= count %></span>
        <p>Includes Active, Adjudicated, Certified, Licensed, Pending, Permitted and Registered water Rights</p>
      </div>
    
      <div class='span3'>
        <span class='large'>Total Water: Active & Permitted Water rights: <%= watermapApp.tally.total_face_amount_active %> AFY, All:
        <%=  watermapApp.addCommas(watermapApp.tally.total_face_amount) %> AFY</span>
        <p>This is the amount that Californians say they will use in a given year. A <a href='http://www.waterboards.ca.gov/waterrights/water_issues/programs/bay_delta/docs/comments111312/tim_stroshane.pdf'>similar value</a> was submitted as a public comment for the Bay Delta plan in October 2012. Value differences are from minor data errors (duplicates, miscategorized entries, etc.)</p>
      </div>
