            <span class='large'>Total Water used in Current Water Rights</span>
            
    
<table id="tally-summary">
  <tr>
    <th>Water Right Status</th>
    <th>Face Value Amount (AFY)</th>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td>Active</td>
    <td><%= watermapApp.addCommas(watermapApp.tally.active) %></td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td>Permitted</td>
    <td><%= watermapApp.addCommas(watermapApp.tally.permitted) %></td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td>Licensed</td>
    <td><%= watermapApp.addCommas(watermapApp.tally.licensed) %></td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td>Adjudicated</td>
    <td><%= watermapApp.addCommas(watermapApp.tally.adjudicated) %></td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td>Certified</td>
    <td><%= watermapApp.addCommas(watermapApp.tally.certified) %></td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td>Pending</td>
    <td><%= watermapApp.addCommas(watermapApp.tally.pending) %></td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td>Registered</td>
    <td><%= watermapApp.tally.registered %></td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td>Total</td>
    <td><%= watermapApp.addCommas(watermapApp.tally.total_face_amount) %></td>
  </tr>
    
</table>

            <p>This is the amount that Californians are permitted to use in a given year. A <a href='http://www.waterboards.ca.gov/waterrights/water_issues/programs/bay_delta/docs/comments111312/tim_stroshane.pdf'>similar value</a> was submitted as a public comment for the Bay Delta plan in October 2012. Value differences are from minor data errors (duplicates, miscategorized entries, etc.)</p>
          </div>
              
          <div class='span3 block observation'>
            <span class='large'>Total Stored: <%=  watermapApp.addCommas(watermapApp.tally.storage) %>AFY</span>
            <p>This is the amount that Californians say they will store in a given year.</p>
          </div>    

          
          <div class='span3 block claim'>
            <span class='large'>Total amount precipitation: ~200,000,000 AFY</span>
            <p>This is the amount precipitation that will fall on California as rain or snow in (2013).</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class='span3 block claim'>
            <span class='large'>Total amount precipitation dedicated for water supply: ~71,000,000 AFY</span>
          </div>
        
          <div class='span3 block observation'>
            <span class='large'>Over-allocated water percentage: <%= overallocation %> </span>
            <h3>What does this mean?</h3>
            <p>This is a rough estimate of how much more water is allocated than comes into the natural water system.</p>
            <p>Some water is reused downstream, some water is over-estimated, and some water is slated for future development.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        
        <div class="span12 block">
          <table id="tally">
            <tr>
              <th id="holder" class="sortable">Water Right Holder</th>
              <th id="amount" class="sortable sortable-numeric reverseSort">Amount (AFY)</th>
            </tr>
            <%- table %>
          </table>
        </div>
        </div>
      </div>
          
      <div id="data-panel" class="tally-content">
        <div id="rights-panel" class="panel">
          <div class="data-boxes">
          <div class="data-box">
            <h4>Water Rights</h4>
            <p>Showing water rights held by individuals, organizations and other entities in the state of California.</p>
            <p>Select a water right to learn more about it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
        
